description: More For Pokemon GO Save battery and improve your Pokemon GO experience with many useful features! Features: * A customizable floating menu with helpful links * An overlay to hide the screen content and block touches to save battery life and make the game - pocket friendly * Dim the screen when you place your device in your pocket to save battery * Auto pocket mode using the proximity sensor * Activate the system built in battery saver when the game launches * Extreme battery saver - make your screen black/white to save battery * Keep the screen on while playing * Kill background processes when the game starts for better performance * Maximize the brightness when the game starts
